{"tid":1364591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[最新防具圖鑑&購買連結] 詳解防具   一齊黎砌史詩裝保家衛港","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:52:19.000Z","uid":105976,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a675786b49e3e472fb244eab8a4829a9d6db95e","tid":1364591,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"入面有分豬嘴 護目鏡 頭盔  身體護具分頁<br />\n有埋購買方法&amp;需知<br />\n另外如果各位已有該防具可以留言講評價<br />\n有新防具推介都請講 盡量更新<br />\n<br />\n打機時見到有1/3手足有口罩 鏡  擋到遠距魔法<br />\n但係冇防具擋唔到對方既<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>物理遠攻</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>和理非既隊友們 你企後面唱聖詩加BUFF都係會被攻擊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最基本既防具 口罩護目鏡都要買  100蚊!</span>  因為前線需要你們係後面加持</strong><br />\n<br />\n口罩可以用200小時+ (戴住黎呼吸先計)  100蚊做到100%防護超抵啦<br />\n用完用密實袋封住<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6c0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=51c55f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n有野記得問 大家幫手答"},{"pid":"5081b3a99c927d5347805081793a30078eb729a3","tid":1364591,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8b0aae67661663d51e63edf5c0e2c3db4780ee","tid":1364591,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c6844d03f6e892ca0aa4f1189b3830acf111e9","tid":1364591,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\